Support
-------

TODO trac specific bug tracking guide

OpenXCAP is developed and supported by AG Projects. AG Projects
offers best-effort gratis support for OpenXCAP. "best-effort" means that
we try to solve the bugs you report or help fix your problems as soon as we
can, subject to available resources.

Installation
------------

Prerequisites:

 - LibXML (http://xmlsoft.org/downloads.html)
 - Python 2.4 or newer (www.python.org)
 - Twisted framework (http://twistedmatrix.com) - Twisted Core and Twisted Web 2
 (TODO check if the tarball is enough, if not, get it from the SVN trunk)
 - lxml (http://codespeak.net/lxml)
 - python-application (TODO)
 
 To enable TLS support, you need:
 - GnuTLS library (http://www.gnu.org/software/gnutls)
 - python-gnutls (http://pypi.python.org/pypi/python-gnutls)
